          <updateDate>2018-04-18T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Immigration Court Improvement Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill expands the definition of &quot;immigration judge&quot; and the requirements applicable to such judges. Specifically, the bill requires that immigration judges have independent decision-making authority and prohibits discipline of such judges for good faith legal decisions. The bill also requires the Department of Justice to promulgate regulations to grant immigration judges contempt power. </p>]]></text>
